IN RE Application of BLACK FORK WIND ENERGY, L.L.C. 2017-0412 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MEDIATION MATTERS

Case returned to the regular docket under S.Ct.Prac.R. 19.01. Appellees shall file a brief within 30 days, and the parties shall otherwise proceed in accordance with S.Ct.Prac.R. 16.02 through 16.07.
